        "class": "",
        "text": "And when the man rose up to depart,.... Rose up from table, having ate and drank sufficiently, in order to depart the house, and proceed on his journey: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "his father in law urged him; with much entreaty, and earnest solicitations, that he would stay all night with him: ",
        "children": []
